.col-md-6
  .card.m-0.mb-5.tip-card
    %h5 You can add a dedicated offer for your service
    %p
      You can add a dedicated offer for your service. Please click “Add new offer”  to create it with all the details
      about your offer, like technical parameters and any other important info. Remember, the more details you give,
      the easier it'll be for potential users to understand what you're offering."

    .card-button.text-center
      = link_to new_offer_link(service, controller_name), "data-e2e": "add-new-offer-btn" do
        %span.btn.btn-outline-secondary.font-weight-bold
          = _("Add new offer")
